## ðŸš€ **Key Takeaways**
âœ… **CRDTs eliminate conflicts in distributed systems.**  
âœ… **G-Counter for increments; PN-Counter for inc/dec.**  
âœ… **Use "merge by max" logic to ensure convergence.**  
âœ… **Ideal for counters, collaborative docs, and shopping carts.**  
âœ… **Integrate via gossip, event sourcing, or pub/sub for real-world use.**  

Want to go deeper? Try **Delta CRDTs** for efficiency or explore **LWW-Registers (Last Write Wins) for timestamped values.**

